data.description: Beautifully updated home that hasnt flooded, with no carpet. Sit and relax on your patio near the inground pool. Acadiana Place off of W Congress with easy access to I-10. This home has it all, curb appeal, location, updates and priced to sell and family fun in the pool. The pool liner  equipment replaced approx.2 1/2 years ago, rear fence replaced 2020, HVAC 4 yrs,, roof 2014, and water heater in 2021.
